[
  {
    "text": "Welcome to round one,\nthe Scooter Shooter.",
    "start": 6.139,
    "duration": 1.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Hop on your scooter,\ngrab your shooter,",
    "start": 7.949,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "and make your way\nthrough four cutouts,",
    "start": 9.959,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "hitting targets along the way.",
    "start": 12.428,
    "duration": 1.641
  },
  {
    "text": "Lowest score is\neliminated from round two.",
    "start": 14.069,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 16.289,
    "duration": 0.975
  },
  {
    "text": "It's no secret, 2020 has\nbeen off to a rough start,",
    "start": 17.264,
    "duration": 2.125
  },
  {
    "text": "had the eye surgery, then\nthe shoulder surgery,",
    "start": 19.389,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "just hoping my doctor is not\na Dude Perfect subscriber.",
    "start": 21.209,
    "duration": 2.292
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, Bob.",
    "start": 23.501,
    "duration": 0.548
  },
  {
    "text": "I ain't no quitter.",
    "start": 24.049,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Really just looking\nforward to the foam pit.",
    "start": 24.959,
    "duration": 1.57
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to do a gainer off of it.",
    "start": 26.529,
    "duration": 1.43
  },
  {
    "text": "If I get to the foam\npit, I'm the true winner.",
    "start": 27.959,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go.",
    "start": 29.959,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 33.399,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude, duck!",
    "start": 34.379,
    "duration": 0.887
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGING]",
    "start": 35.266,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "He fit.",
    "start": 35.849,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's through.",
    "start": 36.349,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 38.779,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow!",
    "start": 39.279,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGING]",
    "start": 39.779,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGING]",
    "start": 46.629,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGING]",
    "start": 49.986,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Clear!",
    "start": 50.569,
    "duration": 0.27
  },
  {
    "text": "All clear.",
    "start": 50.839,
    "duration": 0.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Not breaking any speed records.",
    "start": 51.529,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!",
    "start": 55.691,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!",
    "start": 56.191,
    "duration": 0.863
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGING]",
    "start": 57.054,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Hit it.",
    "start": 57.637,
    "duration": 0.964
  },
  {
    "text": "He hit it.",
    "start": 58.601,
    "duration": 0.964
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 61.499,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "So close, Ty.",
    "start": 62.233,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, man.",
    "start": 64.403,
    "duration": 0.791
  },
  {
    "text": "He went empty.",
    "start": 65.194,
    "duration": 1.005
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 68.043,
    "duration": 1.386
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 69.429,
    "duration": 0.612
  },
  {
    "text": "Heads up!",
    "start": 70.041,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 75.099,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That is harder than\nit looks, boys!",
    "start": 78.699,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember, you just\ncan't be last.",
    "start": 80.769,
    "duration": 1.685
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the goal here.",
    "start": 82.454,
    "duration": 0.875
  },
  {
    "text": "That was as last\nminute as you can get.",
    "start": 90.719,
    "duration": 2.505
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my.",
    "start": 95.049,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No, it doesn't count.",
    "start": 95.549,
    "duration": 0.49
  },
  {
    "text": "Why?",
    "start": 96.039,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He didn't lift his arm.",
    "start": 96.539,
    "duration": 0.972
  },
  {
    "text": "He didn't lift his arm.",
    "start": 97.511,
    "duration": 0.958
  },
  {
    "text": "You're right.",
    "start": 98.469,
    "duration": 0.39
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm amazing at this!",
    "start": 98.859,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 101.629,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to turn around.",
    "start": 103.069,
    "duration": 1.67
  },
  {
    "text": "You're out shots, you noob.",
    "start": 104.739,
    "duration": 1.87
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 106.609,
    "duration": 1.466
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm out of ammo, so I'm just\ngoing to bust through them.",
    "start": 108.075,
    "duration": 2.333
  },
  {
    "text": "I think you should.",
    "start": 110.408,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "And he didn't get\nany points for that.",
    "start": 113.536,
    "duration": 1.583
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 115.119,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Effort.",
    "start": 115.659,
    "duration": 0.265
  },
  {
    "text": "I ain't no quitter.",
    "start": 115.924,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "Unbelieavble.",
    "start": 118.795,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 124.119,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "We have contact.",
    "start": 125.099,
    "duration": 0.79
  },
  {
    "text": "He's out.",
    "start": 127.364,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's out.",
    "start": 127.864,
    "duration": 1.155
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!",
    "start": 129.019,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "He did not.",
    "start": 129.799,
    "duration": 0.89
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 130.689,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "He came out of his left shoe.",
    "start": 131.229,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "Darn it!",
    "start": 133.324,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Made it through the first one.",
    "start": 136.769,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "That almost knocked me\noff the scooter there.",
    "start": 138.799,
    "duration": 2.19
  },
  {
    "text": "Breaking news.",
    "start": 143.769,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Breaking news, drew blood.",
    "start": 144.399,
    "duration": 1.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 146.149,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "This guy drew blood.",
    "start": 146.649,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!",
    "start": 147.482,
    "duration": 0.647
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 148.129,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Nose blood.",
    "start": 148.809,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "From what?",
    "start": 149.609,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "As with every freeze-frame\nvideo, blood is drawn.",
    "start": 150.109,
    "duration": 3.255
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 157.409,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He got three.",
    "start": 157.909,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "There were some\ncatastrophic failures.",
    "start": 158.576,
    "duration": 1.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I think everything\nwas a catastrophic failure.",
    "start": 160.159,
    "duration": 2.66
  },
  {
    "text": "But good news, round two.",
    "start": 162.819,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "We made it.",
    "start": 165.619,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Three.",
    "start": 166.619,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's done it.",
    "start": 169.629,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "If he doesn't get to\nfinish, what then?",
    "start": 176.057,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that was a funny finish.",
    "start": 177.682,
    "duration": 1.237
  },
  {
    "text": "The scooter and him has\nto cross the finish line.",
    "start": 178.919,
    "duration": 2.262
  },
  {
    "text": "He has not crossed\nthe finish line.",
    "start": 181.181,
    "duration": 1.458
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 182.639,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "They're huddling.",
    "start": 183.139,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "He just hit a grand slam, and\nhe didn't touch home plate.",
    "start": 183.859,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "start": 185.879,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "What a shame, though, it'd be\nif eight points didn't get you--",
    "start": 186.389,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 188.959,
    "duration": 0.14
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 189.099,
    "duration": 0.71
  },
  {
    "text": "--to the second round.",
    "start": 189.809,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you think are\nkey moments in a race?",
    "start": 190.859,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 193.939,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no, he's--",
    "start": 194.439,
    "duration": 0.67
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 195.109,
    "duration": 0.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 195.249,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's sinking in.",
    "start": 195.749,
    "duration": 0.902
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 196.651,
    "duration": 1.206
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 197.857,
    "duration": 0.565
  },
  {
    "text": "I think there's an element--",
    "start": 198.422,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 199.589,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's over!",
    "start": 200.089,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "The guy's taking\nhis scooter away.",
    "start": 200.629,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Done.",
    "start": 202.329,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "There's not a victory\nwithout a fight.",
    "start": 203.289,
    "duration": 2.9
  },
  {
    "text": "There's not a sunrise\nwithout a night.",
    "start": 206.189,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Without a sun.",
    "start": 208.769,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "There's not a purchase\nwithout a cost.",
    "start": 209.789,
    "duration": 3.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And there's not a\ncrown without a cross.",
    "start": 213.359,
    "duration": 2.925
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why we're going\nto let him go through.",
    "start": 216.284,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "If you were going\nto see the foam pit,",
    "start": 218.159,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "let's say goodbye to\nhim, get him out of here.",
    "start": 219.819,
    "duration": 2.078
  },
  {
    "text": "Get some ice.",
    "start": 221.897,
    "duration": 0.542
  },
  {
    "text": "He's bringing down everything.",
    "start": 222.439,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "I agree.",
    "start": 223.409,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And let's go foam pit.",
    "start": 223.919,
    "duration": 1.105
  },
  {
    "text": "I love you all.",
    "start": 225.024,
    "duration": 0.625
  },
  {
    "text": "Heal up fast.",
    "start": 225.649,
    "duration": 0.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 226.299,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Hey, hey, hey--",
    "start": 226.799,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER] See ya, dude.",
    "start": 227.679,
    "duration": 0.32
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) --goodbye.",
    "start": 227.999,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 228.759,
    "duration": 0.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my.",
    "start": 228.919,
    "duration": 0.53
  },
  {
    "text": "He almost ran into that thing.",
    "start": 229.449,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to round\ntwo, where, in order",
    "start": 232.679,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "to see the cut-out coming\nat you from behind,",
    "start": 234.269,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "you must knock down the targets\nin front of the TV monitor that",
    "start": 236.489,
    "duration": 3.18
  },
  {
    "text": "will show you which\npose to match,",
    "start": 239.669,
    "duration": 2.099
  },
  {
    "text": "and hit that pose before being\nknocked off into the foam pit.",
    "start": 241.768,
    "duration": 3.241
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 245.009,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Going to be honest, this is a\nlittle higher than I thought,",
    "start": 245.639,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "but I'm excited.",
    "start": 248.159,
    "duration": 0.677
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's do this.",
    "start": 248.836,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
    "start": 249.419,
    "duration": 1.642
  },
  {
    "text": "your hands up.",
    "start": 251.061,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 251.644,
    "duration": 0.445
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 252.089,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Two whites down.",
    "start": 253.089,
    "duration": 0.77
  },
  {
    "text": "He's not going to go for it?",
    "start": 253.859,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Look it.",
    "start": 255.699,
    "duration": 0.61
  },
  {
    "text": "See, here it comes, boy.",
    "start": 256.309,
    "duration": 2.149
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERS]",
    "start": 258.458,
    "duration": 1.389
  },
  {
    "text": "I did forget to\ndrop the blaster.",
    "start": 262.629,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "That would've helped.",
    "start": 264.009,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,\ntwo points for Cory.",
    "start": 264.909,
    "duration": 2.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Been waiting all day\nfor the foam pit,",
    "start": 267.439,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "and here I am on\nthe plank myself.",
    "start": 269.139,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't want to\nfall in because that",
    "start": 271.269,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "means I'll get more points, but\nthen, at the end of the day,",
    "start": 272.769,
    "duration": 1.83
  },
  {
    "text": "it's like, that's\nwhat a foam pit's for.",
    "start": 274.599,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm conflicted.",
    "start": 276.309,
    "duration": 0.662
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 276.971,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 282.179,
    "duration": 0.61
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, he--",
    "start": 282.789,
    "duration": 0.605
  },
  {
    "text": "He needs it.",
    "start": 283.394,
    "duration": 0.685
  },
  {
    "text": "He needs it.",
    "start": 284.079,
    "duration": 1.155
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 286.402,
    "duration": 0.979
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 287.381,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's down.",
    "start": 287.881,
    "duration": 0.986
  },
  {
    "text": "See ya.",
    "start": 288.867,
    "duration": 1.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Right there.",
    "start": 290.346,
    "duration": 1.228
  },
  {
    "text": "The mirror got him.",
    "start": 291.574,
    "duration": 1.055
  },
  {
    "text": "The wrong way with it.",
    "start": 292.629,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you kidding me?",
    "start": 294.369,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "'Sup, guys?",
    "start": 295.589,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty here, getting ready do a\nback flip aerial triple salchow.",
    "start": 296.089,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 298.589,
    "duration": 0.65
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm kidding.",
    "start": 299.239,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I'm not.",
    "start": 299.739,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm just about to\nhit two targets.",
    "start": 300.239,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Actually, I'm going to\nprobably hit three, and then",
    "start": 301.699,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "nail the freeze-frame.",
    "start": 303.039,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "See if I'm a fortuneteller.",
    "start": 303.939,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh-- oh, he got-- oh, he got it.",
    "start": 308.209,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "It didn't fall.",
    "start": 309.589,
    "duration": 1.064
  },
  {
    "text": "He got it!",
    "start": 310.653,
    "duration": 0.922
  },
  {
    "text": "He did.",
    "start": 311.575,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He almost got it.",
    "start": 315.867,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "Dude, you were so close.",
    "start": 317.763,
    "duration": 1.261
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, he's totally gone.",
    "start": 319.024,
    "duration": 1.715
  },
  {
    "text": "He's buried.",
    "start": 320.739,
    "duration": 0.67
  },
  {
    "text": "TT in the finale.",
    "start": 321.409,
    "duration": 1.792
  },
  {
    "text": "What a performance.",
    "start": 323.201,
    "duration": 0.824
  },
  {
    "text": "TT is moving on.",
    "start": 324.025,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 325.661,
    "duration": 1.238
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, let's be real.",
    "start": 326.899,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Two points for both\nGarrett and Cory.",
    "start": 328.069,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel like just a boom,\nboom, boom, and then a--",
    "start": 330.049,
    "duration": 2.126
  },
  {
    "text": "[CLICK]",
    "start": 332.175,
    "duration": 0.838
  },
  {
    "text": "[CRICKETS]",
    "start": 333.013,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "--probably take\nme to the finale.",
    "start": 333.513,
    "duration": 1.306
  },
  {
    "text": "That's just my prediction.",
    "start": 334.819,
    "duration": 1.083
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 338.319,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 341.579,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "You got to have the pose.",
    "start": 342.889,
    "duration": 1.654
  },
  {
    "text": "[DINGING]",
    "start": 344.543,
    "duration": 0.984
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERS]",
    "start": 345.527,
    "duration": 0.984
  },
  {
    "text": "He does it!",
    "start": 347.987,
    "duration": 1.476
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my.",
    "start": 349.463,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "The dream is alive.",
    "start": 351.431,
    "duration": 1.878
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my goodness.",
    "start": 353.309,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Coby and TT in the finale.",
    "start": 354.899,
    "duration": 3.183
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, who do you cheer\nfor in that scenario?",
    "start": 358.082,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "No one, neither.",
    "start": 359.999,
    "duration": 1.613
  },
  {
    "text": "What's up, guys?",
    "start": 361.612,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "You probably know us, by\nnow, as the 'Nale Bros.",
    "start": 362.279,
    "duration": 2.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, good to be here.",
    "start": 364.539,
    "duration": 0.945
  },
  {
    "text": "Great to be here too.",
    "start": 365.484,
    "duration": 0.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 366.359,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "First win 2020 for\nyou, you think?",
    "start": 367.289,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "First and only?",
    "start": 369.329,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, very likely.",
    "start": 370.139,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Very likely?",
    "start": 370.919,
    "duration": 0.61
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 371.529,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 372.029,
    "duration": 0.15
  },
  {
    "text": "Here in the finale, we have\nto shoot six possible targets",
    "start": 372.179,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "while avoiding three\ndifferent frames coming",
    "start": 374.609,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "at us in the process.",
    "start": 376.859,
    "duration": 0.905
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoo.",
    "start": 377.764,
    "duration": 0.425
  },
  {
    "text": "Most points is the winner.",
    "start": 378.189,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Cobes, good luck to you.",
    "start": 379.169,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Best of luck, sir.",
    "start": 380.099,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, absolutely.",
    "start": 380.759,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "Gah, I wanted to push you\ninto that foam pit so bad.",
    "start": 381.467,
    "duration": 2.482
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought about pushing\nyou, just so you know.",
    "start": 383.949,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 389.209,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Does he have to reload?",
    "start": 389.709,
    "duration": 1.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 390.779,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 391.289,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my goodness.",
    "start": 391.789,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Jump!",
    "start": 395.459,
    "duration": 0.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 395.989,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 396.489,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "You got to reload.",
    "start": 397.119,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "He's out of ammo.",
    "start": 397.869,
    "duration": 0.74
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 400.959,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "You got to pull back up.",
    "start": 401.589,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 402.639,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "What a performance.",
    "start": 404.277,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 405.069,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's not there yet.",
    "start": 405.569,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "It's gonna break.",
    "start": 406.361,
    "duration": 0.718
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 408.451,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERS]",
    "start": 410.319,
    "duration": 0.912
  },
  {
    "text": "Front flip, front flip!",
    "start": 411.231,
    "duration": 2.088
  },
  {
    "text": "Yay.",
    "start": 413.319,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERS]",
    "start": 414.219,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "What a performance.",
    "start": 414.779,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys, I paid the price.",
    "start": 416.499,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "A little scrapage there,\nbut that's the price",
    "start": 418.359,
    "duration": 2.85
  },
  {
    "text": "you pay for victory, hopefully.",
    "start": 421.209,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty got through all the\ncut-outs and three targets.",
    "start": 422.629,
    "duration": 2.61
  },
  {
    "text": "That's 12 points total.",
    "start": 425.239,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "As you guys saw, Ty put up\na near-perfect performance.",
    "start": 427.299,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Right now, I am\nvisualizing reading",
    "start": 430.179,
    "duration": 2.31
  },
  {
    "text": "all of your comments\nof support right now.",
    "start": 432.489,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Team Coby, you guys\nare banding together.",
    "start": 435.489,
    "duration": 1.843
  },
  {
    "text": "And I appreciate them.",
    "start": 437.332,
    "duration": 0.917
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to need\nevery single one.",
    "start": 438.249,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's time to\nlight up these targets",
    "start": 439.809,
    "duration": 1.938
  },
  {
    "text": "and jump through these holes,\nyou know what I'm saying?",
    "start": 441.747,
    "duration": 2.292
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's get it.",
    "start": 444.039,
    "duration": 0.542
  },
  {
    "text": "First one's out.",
    "start": 446.221,
    "duration": 1.198
  },
  {
    "text": "Second one's out.",
    "start": 447.419,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Unbelievable.",
    "start": 448.319,
    "duration": 0.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 450.373,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[DING]",
    "start": 450.873,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 454.31,
    "duration": 0.982
  },
  {
    "text": "[DING]",
    "start": 457.449,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Still got a shot left, right?",
    "start": 457.949,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 459.209,
    "duration": 0.24
  },
  {
    "text": "He needs it, he needs it.",
    "start": 459.449,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERS]",
    "start": 461.59,
    "duration": 0.954
  },
  {
    "text": "[BUZZER]",
    "start": 462.544,
    "duration": 0.954
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 463.498,
    "duration": 1.431
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my.",
    "start": 464.929,
    "duration": 1.431
  },
  {
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen--",
    "start": 466.36,
    "duration": 0.954
  },
  {
    "text": "[DINGING]",
    "start": 467.314,
    "duration": 0.954
  },
  {
    "text": "--Tyler is your winner.",
    "start": 468.268,
    "duration": 3.095
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 471.363,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
    "start": 473.126,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he might need to go to\nconcussion protocol after that.",
    "start": 473.959,
    "duration": 3.675
  }
]